Juniper Mirroring Configuration Utility
=======================================


The setFilter.pl tool allows people to modify the
traffic mirroring facilities provided by Juniper
Networks switches as described in the following paper:

L.Deri, Passively Monitoring Networks at Gigabit Speeds
Using Commodity Hardware and Open Source Software, 
PAM 2003 conference and available from http://luca.ntop.org/

As described in the paper, ntop/nProbe and Juniper switches
have been succesfully used to monitor Gbit networks.

---
Luca Deri <deri@ntop.org> - February 2003
